title: Unsupported marker
body:
### Is there an existing issue for this?

- [X] I have searched the existing issues

### Bug description

Terminal log shows unsupported marker when running **analyze_videos**. While the output analysis was still successfully produced, I am wondering if those warnings should be taken care of. Thank you!

### Operating System

Windows 10

### DeepLabCut version

dlc version 2.2.2

### DeepLabCut mode

single animal

### Device type

CPU

### Steps To Reproduce

In DEEPLABCUT environment, ipython, I ran the command like this:

> dlc.analyze_videos('Z:\...\...\config.yaml',['Z:\......\video1.mj2','Z:\......\video1.mj2'],save_as_csv=True)

Note that my video is in .mj2 video type.
